太子有無辜市民被殺害了</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾啦，係支共命令&quot;止暴制亂&quot;之下，明知一日拖一日尤其頭七都唔交出足本只會愈拖愈亂，咁都唔交你地話點解呢？？？？</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加埋依家毛EE爆料，831事件冇人死？？？<br />\n<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFYI，當晚現場傳第一消息：有人打死人，但唔係香港警察，你話係邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？！！！</span></span></span></strong></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a9c9ca8358cc7763612df50bdcfd10fe4caeb54d","tid":1560630,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5bdd85be5d35bcfd3a3a9852acb5cdece591025","tid":1560630,"uid":259984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:36:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9f5e366538b27808f331e5f607da6f04bc3d050e","tid":1560630,"uid":259984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"自推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaeed7e019ef6a104c0007dd4853e90c695a523a","tid":1560630,"uid":248098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n821<br />\n831<br />\nchinazi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a677c4c12be91b1cfadf2adb08bd7d6e19753a4","tid":1560630,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"【保民聯】建制保皇 建設保民 香港值得更好的建設派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560300</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},